Add ideas for functions here:
Function names with (DONE) next to them are finished functions. Add your name next to the functions you made.
- e.g:
- def sample_function(test: str) -> str: (DONE)
Functions with docstrings (that is, the comments in triple quotes [''' or """] ) are functions that aren't completed yet. 
REFER TO THIS IF YOU WRITE CODE: https://peps.python.org/pep-0008/#descriptive-naming-styles

